{"TopicId":167597,"ForumId":20,"TopicTitle":"Experiment Storage Unit and USI-LS","CreatedByName":"kerbalfreak","CreatedById":181766,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-11-16T22:24:28Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"kerbalfreak","CreatedById":181766,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-11-16T22:24:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m looking for mods that have alternatives for the\u00A0Experiment Storage Unit, like the one in Feline Rovers. I find the stock one to be hard to fit nicely in rockets and other vehicles. Would like a radial and/or a stack one. Can have the same size and weight, only a alternative model, preferentially stock-a-like.\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nEdit: I found that the \u0022RC-001S Remote Guidance Unit\u0022, and other 2 pods,can store science in the same way the\u00A0Experiment Storage Unit. Still looking for a radial part that looks beter than the stock one.\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nAnd some more radial containers for \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Umbra Space Industries (a collection of mods)\u0022\u003EUSI\u003C/abbr\u003E-LS also would be nice.\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nDo you know mods that have this features?\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nThanks!!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-11-17T01:31:38Z\u0022 title=\u002211/17/2017 01:31  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00226 yr\u0022\u003ENovember 17, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by kerbalfreak\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"sebi.zzr","CreatedById":81294,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-11-17T10:41:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223221097\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022167597\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221510